        "timestamp": "2019-08-12 17:06:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nBuild Failed \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/dcaegen2-platform-servicechange-handler-release-verify/3/ : FAILURE\n\nNo problems were identified. If you know why this problem occurred, please add a suitable Cause for it. ( https://jenkins.onap.org/job/dcaegen2-platform-servicechange-handler-release-verify/3/ )\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/dcaegen2-platform-servicechange-handler-release-verify/3",
